    "discriminators": [
     "'Not requiring power' is a measurable claim: there is NO sustained tonal motor bed. Low harmonicity and low sustain_ratio are the near-gate priors that keep TOOLPowr and TOOLPneu out.",
     "Morphology is impulsive metal handling: hammer strikes, ratchet clicks, plier snaps, a wrench set on a bench. Bright, spiky, moderately ringing (it is metal, so decay runs longer than wood).",
